room_title: Escape room "Spy Vs Spy" by Escape The Room Oregon in Eugene
room_description: The year is 1988: the height of the cold war. A Russian spy has infiltrated the US. I am with the CIA. The government needs your help finding stolen top-secret material. Can you infiltrate the spies apartment and get back what was stolen? You only have 60 minutes until the spy returns home and catches you.
